                     <interp inst="t18210912-80-person870" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was present when the pepper was laden on board the ship; the bags were in a proper and entire state.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I found the pepper loose.</p>
